snippet.title: Fashion Critic Reacts to Emma Chamberlain's Outfits Of The Week (7 Days, 7 Looks Vogue)
snippet.description:
You can get 60% off your first 4 bottle box from Bright Cellars by using this link: https://www.brightcellars.com/hautelemode/

Emma Chamberlain is one of the biggest stars in the Youtube atmosphere. Her quirky yet relatable vlogs have influenced millions and her rise to fame has showcased the very best of what Youtube has to offer. She is a fashion, lifestyle, and beauty vlogger who has also amassed a huge following on Youtube, Tik Tok, & Instagram, while also being a pioneer of the VSCO girl aesthetic. Emma's clothing choices in this video move from every day wear one might see on your favorite Instagram model to vibrant and whimsical ensembles filled with up-and-coming designers. Through this video, she proves that her clothing hauls that are watched with dedication are nothing to scoff at, but rather a refreshing expression of taste that might not always be understood or respected.
